        </div>
        <div id="how" class="section">
            <h2>How I Do It</h2>
            <p>I use a step-by-step process to clean your BBQ grills thoroughly:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Inspect the grill for any damage or wear.</li>
                <li>Remove grates and other removable parts.</li>
                <li>Soak and scrub the grates using eco-friendly cleaning solutions.</li>
                <li>Clean the interior and exterior of the grill.</li>
                <li>Reassemble the grill and conduct a final inspection.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
